VAR LINE-WIDTH 20 2C,
VAR EMITPOS 7FFF 2C,
MCREATE EMIT
WORDDEF
MKLABEL LINERETURN
DUP LIT 11 2C, <> 0BRANCH LINERETURN WRITELABEL
EMITPOS @ LIT 1 2C, + DUP EMITPOS ! SWAP LIT F000 2C, + SWAP !
EXIT
SETLABEL LINERETURN
DROP EMITPOS @ LINE-WIDTH @ / LINE-WIDTH @ * LIT 20 2C, + EMITPOS ! EXIT

