MCREATE REGISTER-INT
WORDDEF
LIT 1 2C,
MKLABEL SEARCH SETLABEL SEARCH
MKLABEL FOUND
MKLABEL NONE
DUP INT-TABLE + @ 0BRANCH FOUND WRITELABEL
LIT 1 2C, + DUP LIT FFFF 2C, <> 0BRANCH NONE WRITELABEL
BRANCH SEARCH WRITELABEL
SETLABEL FOUND
DUP >R INT-TABLE + ! R> EXIT
SETLABEL NONE
DROP DROP
LIT FFFF 2C, EXIT

